### 2. Prepare your revealjs presentation slides (HTML file) using Quarto

When you prepare the Quarto report,  implement as many features and effects of the HTML format as you can, including, but not limited to, the following:

1.  <div>

    1.  Incremental lists

    2.  Manual Incremental

    3.  Content overflow

    4.  Columns

    5.  Speaker notes

    6.  Footer & Logo

    7.  Content overflow

    8.  Speaker notes

    9.  Asides & Footnotes

    10. Footer & Logo

    11. Title slides

    12. Slide transition

    13. Fragments

    14. Using ready-made themes

    15. Customizing theme

    16. Creating themes

    17. Using Sass variables / CSS

    18. References / citations

    </div>

